      "rationale": "At MRL 2, formal numerical solver error quantification beyond iterative convergence monitoring is not required. Residuals converged to 1e-6 for all transport equations. Imbalance in mass and momentum < 0.01%. Factor scoped to minimum required level."
    },
    {
