      "rationale": "Formal use error assessment not required at MRL 2. Lead analyst holds PhD in biofluid mechanics with 8 years CFD experience in cardiovascular devices. Simulation protocol reviewed by independent senior analyst prior to production runs. Qualification records archived."
    },
    {
