      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published performance for confined rotating flows (Benim et al. 2011, Fraser et al. 2018). Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power law selected per FDA guidance precedent. Formal model form uncertainty quantification deferred per MRL 2 scoping."
    },
    {
