      "rationale": "Blood viscosity (0.0035 Pa·s), density (1060 kg/m³), and power-law hemolysis coefficients (C=3.62e-7, α=2.416, β=0.785) sourced from peer-reviewed literature. Sensitivity to ±10% variation in hemolysis coefficients evaluated qualitatively; formal UQ not required at MRL 2."
