      "rationale": "Bovine blood sourced from certified abattoir, processed within 6 hours of collection. Hematocrit adjusted to 33% by centrifugation per ASTM F1841. Three independent blood lots used across the 5-point test matrix. Inter-lot variability < 8% for MIH measurements. Formal statistical sample size analysis deferred at MRL 2."
    },
