      "rationale": "Computational boundary conditions (inlet velocity profiles, outlet pressure, wall motion) derived directly from experimental measurements. Qualitative equivalency confirmed by comparison of pump head-flow curves between CFD and experiment (maximum deviation 6.2%). Formal input parameter equivalency metric not required at MRL 2."
